cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with control design for orbital robotic capture of a non-cooperative Target. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper develops a model-based observer for Target kinematics/dynamics. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible category as the paper uses exteroceptive sensors for relative pose measurements. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses a nonlinear observer for estimation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper develops an internal model for Target kinematics/dynamics.
